data.title: Strut Your Mutt - Ellis County - SPCA of Texas
data.meta_description: Get ready to strut your stuff with your furry best friend at Strut Your Mutt, The Race to End Animal Cruelty.
data.text:
Get ready to strut your stuff with your furry best friend at Strut Your Mutt, The Race to End Animal Cruelty. Strutters can participate in the 1.5K fun run as an individual or part of a team. Plus, enjoy family-friendly food, drink and entertainment.

The Bow Wow Bazaar will include vendor booths, activities for pets and kids, demonstrations and more!

Strut Your Mutt, The Race to End Animal Cruelty, supports the lifesaving work that SPCA of Texas does every day. After animals are removed from harm, they still have a long road to recovery ahead of them. Our staff focuses on providing compassionate rehabilitation and healing so the thousands of animals we care for each year can find their loving forever homes.
